ModulePrefs.title: RevelDigital Clock App
ModulePrefs.description: Clock with EnumValues for multiple time zones and automatic localization.
ModulePrefs.author: RevelDigital

Module.Content:
<style type="text/css">
                html
				{
                    width: __UP_rdW__px;
                    height: __UP_rdH__px;
                }
				body, app-root
				{
					background: transparent;
					width: __UP_rdW__px;
					height: __UP_rdH__px;
					overflow: hidden;
					background-color: #__UP_BackColor__;
				}
            </style>
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://reveldigital.github.io/reveldigital-gadgets/apps/ng-clock-app/styles.28f1c5685c9cf4b085d6.css">
            <body>
            	<app-root></app-root>
			
				<script src="https://reveldigital.github.io/reveldigital-gadgets/apps/ng-clock-app/runtime-es2015.9219b05665a619368e7c.js" type="module"></script>
				<script src="https://reveldigital.github.io/reveldigital-gadgets/apps/ng-clock-app/runtime-es5.9219b05665a619368e7c.js" nomodule defer></script>

				<script type="text/javascript">

					var prefs = new gadgets.Prefs();
					
					function load() {
						WebFont.load({
							google: {
								families: [ gadgets.reveldigital.getFamilyName(prefs.getString("body-style")) ]
							}
						});
					}
					gadgets.util.registerOnLoadHandler(load);
					
				</script>
